All services are running correctly. Let me do a final verification of the nginx proxy and confirm the desktop is still active.

{
  "analysis": "All services verified: QEMU running (PID 3650), VNC on 5901, websockify on 6080, nginx on port 80, monitor socket active, keyboard input working, VM status running. The Windows 3.11 desktop is loaded at 1024x768. Need to verify nginx proxy and final state.",
  "plan": "Final verification: check nginx proxy works, take one more screenshot to confirm desktop is still up, verify snapshot mode.",
